name: what'smyfortune
0:
”Alexa Open What's My Fortune”
”Tell me my fortune”
”What is my fortune”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: what's my fortune
des:
Bored? Uncertain about the future? Introducing....Alexa's new skill: Fortune!

That's right: Alexa can now tell you your fortune!

Let Alexa unravel the murky depths of what lies ahead... in the FUTURE!

Why suffer the perils of uncertainty when Alexa's powers of mystic clairvoyance can soothe your troubled soul with her deep, well-thought out, and sometimes humorous fortunes.

From relationship and health suggestions, to the weather, to sarcastic (but good-natured) jokes, Alexa knows it all. 

Having your fortune told has never been so satisfying, fun and snarky!

But she isn't infallible.

Fortune telling is an inexact art, and Alexa, being a robot, is especially prone to mistakes and is certainly not a master of interpreting the mysterious vibrations involved in telling the future.

(So feedback is always welcome, and future versions of the skill will be with updated with ideas from user feedback!)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
